en_55250_0	Functions were organized in all Provinces parallel to the national ceremony organized for the opening of 250 school buildings.
en_55250_1	The Western Province was held at the Prince College in Kotahena under the aegis of Minister Ravi Karunanayake.
en_55250_2	The opening of the school building of the Chandrika Wewa Jayanthi Maha Vidyalaya of the Sabaragamuwa Province took place under the patronage of United National Party Kolonnawa electoral organizer P. Abeynayake.
en_55250_3	Meanwhile the Central Province ceremony was held at the Kandy Bathiuideen Mahmud Balika Vidyalaya.
en_55250_4	It school building was opened by Minister Lakshman Kiriella.
en_55250_5	Th Northwestern Province function was held at the Puttalam Hindu College under the patronage of Parliamentarian Hector Appuhamy.
en_55250_6	The Southern Province event was held at the Galle Sudharma Maha Vidyalaya.
en_55250_7	It took place under the guidance of Minister Vajira Abeywardena.
en_55250_8	The Northern Province event was held at the Oddusudan Maha Vidyalaya in Mullaitivu.
en_55250_9	The building was opened by Parliamentarian Shanthini Skandaraja.
en_55250_10	The Eastern Province function was organized at the Kinniya Meera Nagara Muslim Vidyalaya.
en_55250_11	It was held under the patronage of Parliamentarian M.S. Fowseek.
